perjalanan kalian berharga

183
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:36,280
dan bermanfaat.

184
00:12:36,290 --> 00:12:37,090
Terima kasih, Ayah.

185
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,300
Terima kasih, Tuan Xiao.

